data.description: Charming Family Home with Modern Comforts* Welcome to your new sanctuary nestled in the serene cul-de-sac of a friendly and peaceful neighborhood! This meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience for modern family living. Key Features: * Spacious Interior: Enter into a bright and airy living space, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. Large windows throughout the home flood the rooms with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. * Modern Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen boasts sleek countertops, ample cabinet space, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. * Comfortable Bedrooms: Retreat to one of four comfortable bedrooms, including a master suite with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. * Hardwood Floors: Elegant hardwood flooring throughout the main living areas adds warmth and sophistication to every room. * Fresh Interior Paint: Step into a bright and inviting atmosphere with freshly painted walls that exude modern charm. * Cul-de-Sac Location: Experience peace and quiet with minimal traffic in a safe and family-friendly environment. Enjoy the best of suburban living with easy access to nearby parks, schools, shopping centers, and major commuter routes. This location offers the perfect balance of tranquility and urban convenience. * Private Outdoor Oasis: Step outside to your own private retreat! The expansive backyard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities. Experience year-round enjoyment in your in-ground, heated saltwater pool, offering relaxation and recreation for the whole family. Hosting summer barbecues or enjoying peaceful evenings under the stars has never been easier. * Screened-In Porch: Enjoy bug-free evenings and tranquil mornings in your private outdoor oasis. * Landscape Lighting: Illuminate your outdoor space beautifully, enhancing the curb appeal and providing added security. * Security System: Rest easy knowing your family and belongings are protected with a comprehensive security system in place. * Privacy Fence: Enjoy ultimate privacy and seclusion in your backyard retreat, perfect for entertaining or relaxing in solitude. * Sprinkler System: Maintain a lush and vibrant lawn effortlessly with a convenient sprinkler system that keeps your landscaping looking its best. * 2-Car Garage: Ample parking and storage space for your vehicles, tools, and outdoor gear. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to make this charming house your forever home! Schedule your showing today and experience the comfort and convenience of suburban living at its finest.
